snippet.title: Shall We Date?: Wizardess Heart + - Light Fildora Chapter 1
snippet.description:
I do not own anything from the video, all rights belong to NTT Solmare!

Hello guys! Sorry for the long hiatus! I’ve been taking a break to focus on completing my studies and now that it’s temporarily over, I found time to continue otome games again c:

Unfortunately I made it back on time to catch this last route’s release because as NTT Solmare announced - Wizardess Heart will be discontinued 🥺 To be frank, I’ll miss this game so much because I’ve been playing it since years ago. Hope you guys will like it!
